---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="About Fix Anything Blog, a beginner-friendly programming blog focused on practical guides for developers and students."
  contentClass="mt-12 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-left md:px-8"
>
  <section class="rounded-[2rem] border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm md:p-10">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-emerald-700">
      About the blog
    </p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-left text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-zinc-900 md:text-5xl">
      Practical notes for developers learning by building.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-zinc-700">
      Fix Anything Blog is for beginner to mid-level developers and students who
      want clear explanations without excessive theory. The goal is simple:
      publish useful guides that help you understand a tool, try it quickly, and
      move on to the next problem with better instincts.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
    <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-left text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">
        What you will find here
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
        <li class="text-left text-base text-zinc-700">Python guides for everyday development tasks.</li>
        <li class="text-left text-base text-zinc-700">AI workflow notes that focus on useful output, not hype.</li>
        <li class="text-left text-base text-zinc-700">Practical references you can revisit when building projects.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-left text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">
        Who this launch is for
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
        <li class="text-left text-base text-zinc-700">Students learning core programming concepts.</li>
        <li class="text-left text-base text-zinc-700">Developers early in their careers who need practical refreshers.</li>
        <li class="text-left text-base text-zinc-700">Readers who prefer concise guides over long documentation dives.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
